<doc id="487288" wikidata="Q5385812" url="?curid=487288" title="Ergodic (disambiguation)">
<text>Aside from its generic use as the generic adjective ergodic, ergodic may relate to:
* Ergodicity, mathematical description of a dynamical system which, broadly speaking, has the same behavior averaged over time as averaged over the space of all the system&#x27;s states (phase space)
* Ergodic hypothesis, a postulate of thermodynamics
* Ergodic theory, a branch of mathematics
* Ergodic literature, literature that requires special effort to navigate
* Ergodic process, a particular type of stochastic processes</text><links>
