* &quot;Why We Need An Actual Revolution And How We Can Really Make Revolution&quot; (2018)
* Three Interviews with Bob Avakian: &quot;Up Close and Personal with Bob Avakian - Heart and Soul &amp; Hard-Core for Revolution&quot; (2023) (Part 1, Part 2 and Part 3)

==In popular culture==
James LeGros portrays Avakian in the 1995 Mario Van Peebles film &quot;Panther&quot;.

